55:02.675 --> 55:05.136
North Valley attacked us.

55:05.261 --> 55:07.555
Their intentions were clear.

55:08.681 --> 55:13.060
They saw us as vulnerable
without Gilberto.

55:13.185 --> 55:15.813
Weak, with me in charge.

55:15.938 --> 55:18.691
