55:20.026 --> 55:22.028
Take what's ours.

55:25.740 --> 55:27.158
I...

55:28.367 --> 55:33.497
All of us know there's only
one appropriate response to this.

55:33.622 --> 55:38.044
One way to react against these people
who want to take everything from us,

55:38.169 --> 55:40.546
what we've worked so hard to build.

55:44.508 --> 55:45.926
War.

55:52.016 --> 55:54.018
This is Gilberto's decision?

55:58.647 --> 55:59.857
It's...

56:00.858 --> 56:02.234
